<i>where strange and warlike beings</i>
<i>were poised on the brink</i>

01:45:24.809 --> 01:45:27.288
<i>of frightful interstellar battle.</i>

01:45:27.392 --> 01:45:31.921
<i>The two opposing leaders, resplendent</i>
<i>in their black-jewelled battle shorts</i>

01:45:32.026 --> 01:45:34.057
<i>were meeting for the last time,</i>

01:45:34.228 --> 01:45:36.969
<i>when a dreadful silence fell.</i>

01:45:37.073 --> 01:45:39.012
<i>And at that very moment,</i>

01:45:39.116 --> 01:45:43.058
<i>the words "I wouldn't want to go</i>
<i>anywhere without my wonderful towel"</i>

01:45:43.237 --> 01:45:46.184
<i>drifted across the conference table.</i>

01:45:46.288 --> 01:45:48.941
<i>Unfortunately, in their native tongue,</i>

01:45:49.045 --> 01:45:52.026
<i>this was the most appalling</i>
<i>insult imaginable.</i>

01:45:52.130 --> 01:45:53.736
<i>So the opposing battle fleets</i>

01:45:53.840 --> 01:45:56.445
<i>decided to settle</i>
<i>their remaining differences,</i>

01:45:56.549 --> 01:45:59.905
<i>in order to launch</i>
<i>a joint attack on our galaxy,</i>

01:46:00.009 --> 01:46:04.121
<i>now positively identified</i>
<i>as the source of the offending remark.</i>

01:46:04.226 --> 01:46:07.466
<i>For thousands of years,</i>
<i>the mighty starships tore across</i>

01:46:07.595 --> 01:46:13.005
<i>the empty wastes of space and finally</i>
<i>dived screaming onto the planet Earth,</i>

01:46:13.109 --> 01:46:17.145
<i>where, due to</i>
<i>a terrible miscalculation of scale,</i>

01:46:17.271 --> 01:46:21.697
<i>the entire battle fleet was</i>
<i>accidentally swallowed by a small dog.</i>

01:46:22.159 --> 01:46:25.734
<i>Those who study the complex</i>
<i>interplay of cause and effect</i>

01:46:25.863 --> 01:46:27.571
<i>in the history of the universe</i>

01:46:27.698 --> 01:46:31.694
<i>say that this sort of thing</i>
<i>is going on all the time.</i>

